verbose_text: While TWEAK inhibits Akt phosphorylation in cultured myotubes [XREF_BIBR], the level of phosphorylation of Akt and its downstream targets was comparable in denervated muscle of wild-type, TWEAK-Tg and TWEAK-KO mice suggesting that the inhibitory effect of TWEAK on PI3K / Akt pathway is neutralized by some other factors that may be present in denervated muscle in vivo [XREF_BIBR].
